casebody.data:
Courtney GREEN
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 14, 2017

Brittany B. Paz, in support of the petition.

The petitioner Courtney Green's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 172 Conn.App. 585, 160 A.3d 1068 (2017), is denied.

McDONALD, J., did not participate in the consideration of or decision on this petition.
